  TraceServerInterface Protocol stub and returns None. This produced a
  phantom 'failure' of the dupe-select test (None.digest AttributeErrors)
  that disappeared on the real top branch. Lesson: ALWAYS check
  git branch --show-current before diagnosing 'failures' in a
  multi-branch stack workspace; gt track/checkout moves HEAD.
